<promed@promedmail.org>
[The above web-site includes 2 additional tables:
(1) Survey of live caught birds to identify the presence of avian
influenza viruses (3343 samples received since the beginning of Nov
2005), and (2) Survey of freshly shot birds to identify the presence
of avian influenza viruses (423 samples received since the beginning
of Nov 2005). Including the species of tested birds to the 3 tables
will be an added value. - Mod.AS]
